<h1>Calvin Correli</h1>

<h2><a href="/">/now</a>: <a href="http://calvincorreli.com/now/">calvincorreli.com/now</a></h2>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
New York
NY
United States
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
Founder of Simplero.  Spiritual mentor to entrepreneurs.  Aspiring singer/songwriter/producer.
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I help people be free to be who they really are.
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
Because I love seeing people break free of their self-imposed prisons.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
You already know who you truly want to become. Latch onto it, and go with it.
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
